Package: clplite
Type: Package
Title: A Lightweight Linear Programming Solver Based on 'Clp'
Version: 0.1.0
Description: A high performance linear programming solver based on the 'Clp'
    library (https://projects.coin-or.org/Clp). Sparse constraints are fully
    supported for solving large-scale problems. Source code of the 'Clp' library
    is included in the package for easy installation.
